    <stitle>EC-17 ANTILOCK TRACTION CONTROLLER - INSTALLING THE EC-17 CONTROLLER - BRACKET MOUNTED EC-17</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="0">
        <title>BRACKET MOUNTED EC-17</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Secure the EC-17 to its bracket using the four hex head bolts. Torque to 98 in-Ibs. (Grade 5
                bolts).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">After noting the positioning marks, mount the EC-17 on the vehicle using the mounting
                hardware retained during removal.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Reconnect the electrical connector(s) to the EC-17 and torque the connector retaining bolts
                to 15-20 inch pounds.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Perform the
                <hotlnk document="s04038_X0403801.xml" xrefid="x0403801">"Initial Start Up Procedure"</hotlnk>
                in the TROUBLESHOOTING section to assure proper system operation.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
